title: Trans Oceanic Magical Cruise
description: It's fun on the high seas as the Titans enjoy a cruise filled with dangerous missions, fast cars, and alien attacks.

title: My Enemy, My Friend
description: The Ice Emperor's terrible Ice Dragon strikes again, laying waste to the Ice Fisher's village, forcing the ninja to go after Lloyd…

title: #RageCat
description: Jessica Cruz is convinced she can find the purr-fect forever home for Dexter, a cat who has been deemed unadoptable because he's basically the worst cat in the world. Her overbearing persistence in trying to get him adopted leads Dexter to become Dex-Starr, an evil Red Lantern supervillain! Can Jess still find the good in a fuzzy little nemesis who is trying to kill her?

title: Banana Joe
description: Cuando el director Brown le asigna a Darwin la tarea de hacer el anuario escolar, Darwin comienza pidiéndole a Banana Joe, el payaso de la clase, una simple selfi para la portada. Pero con Banana Joe, las cosas nunca son tan simples.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Ain't That a Kick in the Side?
description: After Witch Way teases Prohyas by calling him, "Vambre's sidekick," Prohyas intensifies his efforts to prove them wrong.

title: Kelsey Quest
description: Kelsey accepts a quest from the Elders of the Creek, but is she ready for her terrifying opponent?

title: Drawn to Sports with Zachary
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Zachary loves competing and developing his skills in karate.

title: Ant We All Just Get Along
description: Owen and Beth try to save an ant hill that Courtney and Leshawna want to destroy.

title: Drawn to Sports with Hannah
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Hannah competes in track and field.

title: El Lamento del Krag
description: Cole despierta en una caverna helada donde habita una bestia legendaria, y en su intento por escapar descubre una sorprendente verdad.

title: Last One There
description: When Unikitty accidentally invokes an ancient curse, the gang must beat Master Frown and Brock back to the castle before one of them literally turns into a rotten egg.

title: Creative Geniuses
description: The Titans visit the Jump City Comic Book Con where they meet Marv Wolfman and George Pérez, but also tangle with Control Freak over an exclusive toy.

title: The Potato
description: When Darwin has lunch with Idaho, he decides to stop eating potatoes in solidarity with his brotato. However, he finds his obsession with his favourite food harder to kick than he ever imagined so Gumball decides to help his friend curb his carb cravings.

title: La Invitacion
description: Craig y sus amigos están invitados a una exclusiva merienda con deliciosos postres, si es que pueden quedarse hasta el final de la fiesta.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Oh, Daisy!
description: Buttercup is not a fan of Bubbles' newly created digital assistant.

title: Block Party
description: Apple and Onion have to outwit a mean duck who's taken over their building's roof.

title: Let's Fight to the End
description: When a fighting tournament is announced at the Plaza, there is more at stake than meets the eye.

title: Mordeby and Rigbecai
description: Mordecai and Rigby mess around with a teleportation machine, and you can pretty much imagine how this one goes.

title: Party Popper
description: Apple and Onion's party plans are interrupted by a grumpy guest.

title: Intravension
description: Los misterios de las Omni-Mejoras se resuelven cuando Ben lucha contra una invasión alienígena proveniente del Omnitrix.

title: The More You Moe, the Moe You Know
description: Moe visits the tree house with a special birthday surprise for BMO. While BMO's mission stands on the brink of disaster, Finn & Jake host a strange guest.

title: The Shelf
description: After Bugs wins the Nobel Prize, he needs a shelf to put it on. Easier said than done.

title: Dog Decider
description: Unable to make tough decisions, Craig decides to put his choices in the hands of a dog named Fred.

title: La Ultima Cambia Formas
description: Akita cuenta la historia de "la Elección" y cómo es que ella y su hermano gemelo, Kataru, fueron al bosque para descubrir su forma animal.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Revienta Fiestas
description: Los planes de la fiesta de Manzana y Cebollín son interrumpidos por un invitado malhumorado.

title: The Unikingdom Awards
description: Unikitty throws an elaborate award show for everyone in the Unikingdom, including Master Frown and Brock, but tensions rise when Frown fails to win an award.

title: Fixing a Flonk
description: Wanting to stop Flonk from being an evildoer for good, Prohyas tries to find Flonk a permanent venue for his nasty comedy. Vambre, however, wants to deliver him to the cops as usual.

title: The Puppets
description: While searching the attic for items to put in their yard sale, Gumball and Darwin stumble upon a load of their old toys. Darwin is especially pleased when he finds his old puppets, Frank and Howdy. However, as Darwin starts playing with them again, Gumball gradually realizes that Frank and Howdy are actually playing with Darwin...

title: Gilben's Different
description: Gilben's newly sprouted peach fuzz sparks a discussion about puberty that ultimately convinces Clarence to act more like an adult.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Brood
description: Craig's determination to get his granddad a cicada shell causes him, Kelsey and JP to become trapped in their stump!

title: Paste Makes Waste/Ice Sore
description: Paste Makes Waste: When Buttercup's taunting turns paste-eating classmate Elmer Sglue into a destructive Paste Monster, she gets out of a sticky situation by doing something against her tough nature, apologizing./Ice Sore: During a heat wave, Blossom discovers that she has a new power: ice breath. But when she doesn't use her new gift wisely, she gets a chilly reception from her sisters.

title: Secret of the Wolf
description: The Ice Emperor summons an enormous ice Behemoth to attack Lloyd and his faithful wolf companion.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Video Cita
description: Panda es un ávido salidor de citas por Internet, y cuando una adorable mujer francesa coincide con él y accede a tener una cita virtual con video, Panda y sus hermanos manejan la situación para poder mostrar su mejor perfil en el video, aunque ese perfil sea absolutamente exagerado.

title: Drawn to Change
description: Cartoon Network is Drawn to Change, and Craig of the Creek talks to Martin Luther King Junior's granddaughter Yolanda about how kids can change the world!

title: Video Date
description: Panda is an avid e-dater, and when a lovely French woman matches with him and agrees to a video chat date. Panda and his brothers engineer the situation so Panda is able to show the best side of himself on the video chat, even if that side of him is completely exaggerated.

title: And Then There Were 10
description: Ben discovers the Omnitrix, and when it attaches itself to Ben's wrist, he discovers it allows him to become any one of ten alien heroes.

title: Friend Ship
description: The Crystal Gems explore an ancient Gem spaceship.

title: Innervasion Part 5: High Override
description: While Ben struggles to avoid the High Override's mind control, Max and Gwen enter the Omnitrix to lend a hand, but once they find Ben is not who he seems, Max and Gwen must pull out all the stops if they are to get Ben back in time to save the planet.

title: Innervasion Part 3: Strange Bedfellows
description: After the Junkbot shoots the Omnitrix and it begins glowing neon-blue, an imprisoned Vilgax explains it is now a gateway through which the Fulmini Empire will invade Earth, but the only way to stop them is from within the Omnitrix, so Ben must team up with the ultimate baddie if he is to save his planet.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: The Music Hole
description: While judging the hugest Battle of the Bands in the history of Ooo, Finn hears a mysterious new song.

title: #GatoRabioso
description: Jessica Cruz está convencida de que puede conseguirle un hogar definitivo perfecto para Dexter, un gato que la gente considera inadoptable porque, básicamente, es el peor gato del mundo.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Sword Heist
description: When a local sword shop sells an ultra powerful sword to Ratar-O, Lion-O decides he has to steal it before Ratar-O can come pick it up. Unfortunately Lion-O is completely against stealing, but luckily he knows someone who loves to steal, Lion-S!

title: The Awesome Brawlers and Haavik/First Fusion! Drago and Tretorous
description: The Awesome Brawlers and Haavik: It's the Haavik Show! Haavik shows up unexpectedly at the practice field and proposes he and Dan play a little game. The Awesome Brawlers have never seen this man before, but they sense something is odd about him. Regardless, when Haavik strokes Dan's ego, there's no way he's backing down from this challenge./First Fusion! Drago and Tretorous: With his back against the wall, Dan tries flipping the script on Haavik by challenging him to a game of his own - a Bakugan Brawl. If Dan wins, then Haavik will have to set him, and the other Awesome Brawler's free.

title: Suitable Armor
description: A veteran warrior insists that Vambre is under dressed for battle and takes it upon herself to garb Vambre in armor as Prohyas fights the beast solo without armor.

title: Muh-Muh-Muh-Murder
description: Daffy suspects Porky might be a murderer.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Manor and Mannerisms
description: Robin attends a ball at Wayne Manor hoping to become heir of the mansion, but will the other Titans spoil his chances?

title: Duo Espinoso
description: Después de dejar Pequeña Escuela Madre, Steven ha encontrado un nuevo pasatiempo: las plantas.

title: Drawn to Sports with Luke
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Luke is passionate about running, jumping and climbing in Ninja Racing.

title: WaterHose-Five
description: The hottest day of the year and a broke air conditioner leads to a water battle of epic proportions to determine who controls the garden hose.

title: Innervasion Part 4: Mind over Alien Matter
description: While inside the Omnitrix, Ben and Vilgax must work together if they are to close the gateway, but once the Fulmini leader, the High Override, appears, even that might not be enough. Luckily, help arrives in the form of a being calling itself Glitch!

title: Summer Showers
description: Jake's daughter Viola is up for a role in a play by a hot new director, Lumpy Space Princess.

title: #TheGoodTheBadAndTheBizarre
description: Everything is going well for Kara Danvers, both as a teen and a superhero, until she starts taking the blame for things she didn't do, and the emergence of a new supervillain threatens to destroy Supergirl's hard-earned reputation.

title: El Trampolin de Hamburguesa
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben encontrar una manera de usar el trampolín de Hamburguesa sin que él se sienta usado.

title: Jethro's All Yours
description: KO gets his first solo mission!

title: Sir Tree's Body
description: Seth wants to help sad, immobile Sir Tree feel the joy that comes from helping others, so he has the brilliant idea of planting Sir Tree inside Pascal's body! But when Sir Tree's absence causes soil erosion and mudslides, Seth has to convince Sir Tree that the best way to help is to return to his hole before Fancytown is destroyed.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Permanent Retirement
description: Grandpa, Gwen and Ben visit an old maid relative only to find that her retirement community has been overtaken by a shapeshifting aliens called Limax.

title: Nature Clarence
description: Clarence, Sumo and Jeff's nature hike veers off course courtesy of their under qualified, overwhelmed guide Josh, prompting Clarence to take the lead.

title: King of the Machines
description: Panthro gets insecure when he finds out Barbastella has a history of dating royalty, so he tries to impress her by becoming "King of the Machines" and giving all the appliances in the Cats' Lair artificial intelligence.

title: Trick or Threat
description: Four kids in Justice League costumes are trick or treating on Halloween when they investigate a spooky house. As dangers befalls them inside, they come to realize that maybe they're not kids at all, but real Justice Leaguers under a spell.

title: Beat Your Greens/Down N' Dirty
description: Beat Your Greens: When Broccoli Aliens from space invade Townsville, it's up to the Powerpuff Girls and all the children of Townsville to take a bite out of crime. Down N' Dirty: When Buttercup refuses to take a bath, the town kicks her out. But Buttercup decides to stick with her stink until her favorite thing is taken away from her.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Compartir es querer
description: Courtney se niega a compartir su valioso juguete de coleccionista con sus amigos.

title: Memory Mayhem
description: Frankie tries to discover more about the mysterious rock that bought them to their new home, with the help of an entity called The Head.

title: Drawn To Expression!
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating queer youth and families in the LGBTQIA+ community that radiate joy, pride, and inclusivity. We are championing the ways these kids and families form connections to their authentic selves by expressing their creativity and queer identity through their art.

title: The Petals
description: When Leslie's petals begin falling off he feels like his good looks are fading, Gumball and Darwin use everything they know about style and beauty to try and help him. The only problem is they know nothing about style or beauty. As Gumball and Darwin's methods become more extreme, Leslie questions whether he's prepared to make the ultimate sacrifice for beauty.

title: La Camada
description: La determinación de Craig de conseguirle a su abuelo un caparazón de cigarra hace que él, Kelsey y JP queden atrapados en su tronco.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: El Arbol del Viajero
description: Carcomido por la culpa por haber perdido el Té del Viajero, cole se embarca en un peligrosa misión haciala cima de una montaña esperando encontrar el legendario Árbol del Viajero, que se supone que está custodiado por una feroz bestia.

title: Dangerous Dealings/The Hunter Returns
description: Dangerous Dealings: The Awesome Brawler's have become aware of a growing number of adults with illegal Baku-brawling devices. But where are they all coming from? Shun decides to take things into his own hands and sets up a "sting" operation to try to draw out the person selling the devices./The Hunter Returns: Lightning has been caught and locked up by an overly aggressive dog catcher! And to make things worse, he doesn't have his collar with Baku-balls. At the compound where he's being held, he runs into an old foe.  It's up to these two enemies to team up and escape their captor.

title: Best Best Friends
description: Master Frown and Brock attend a friendship-themed competition intending to ruin it for everyone else, but soon discover their own friendship in need of repair.

title: Little Graduation
description: Steven and the Gems celebrate Little Homeschool's first graduating class.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Y todos nos llevamos bien
description: Owen y Beth tratan de salvar un hormiguero que Courtney y Leshawna quieren destruir.

title: Chloe and Ice Bear
description: On a day out with just Ice Bear, Chloe realizes Ice Bear only runs errands for his brothers. Determined to show him a fun day in the city, Chloe promises to help Ice Bear have a good time, even if it means staying  in a museum after it closes.

title: Manzana, Concentrate
description: Manzana ayuda a Cebollín a cumplir su sueño de competir en un programa de pastelería.

title: The Puppet Awesome Brawlers/The Return of Sophie
description: The Puppet Awesome Brawlers: The Awesome brawlers go to see Benton Dusk to tell him about the Fusion Bakugan and ask him if he knows anything about this character: Haavik. However, the meeting takes an unexpected twist when Haavik decides to crash it./The Return of Sophie: A video has surfaced showing Toshi using an illegal Baku-Brawling device! Shun has his hands full when Sophie starts making trouble for Kazami Holdings, accusing them of illegally exploiting Bakugan.

title: Sonrie y Aguanta
description: Cuando un dolor de muelas envía a Axel al dentista, el equipo debe luchar contra la Princesa SugarSalt, quien confunde la nueva "corona" de Axel con la realidad.

title: The Last of the Formlings
description: Akita tells the story of the "Choosing" and how she, and her twin brother, Kataru, went into the wilds to discover their animal forms.

title: Madtrap
description: Madcap and Princess SugarSalt trap Axel and the team inside a Minergy-powered labyrinth that attacks them with their greatest fears, forcing them to work together and escape as a unit.

title: Escaramuza
description: When Val's favorite Escaramuza team loses a member, he convinces Xochi to join the squad. He becomes her coach and will do anything to win the big competition.

title: Onion Friend
description: Steven and Amethyst visit the strange world of Onion's house.

title: La Tienda De Cupcakes
description: Quando o adorado computador dos ursos quebra, os três são obrigados a fazer algo que nunca haviam feito antes: arrumar um emprego. Eles começam a trabalhar numa loja badalada de cupcakes e se dão conta de que o mercado profissional é muito mais penoso do que achavam.

title: #BackInAFlash
description: After an embarrassing incident ruins Barbara Gordon's reputation, rather than owning it and moving on, she decides it's easier to harness The Flash's newly discovered ability to travel back in time and alter the delicate fabric of the space-time continuum.

title: Journey to Maize Mountain Part 1
description: When Vic & Val destroy Monte Macabre's corn supply, they travel with Sal to Corn Mountain to replace it. But in order to get the corn, they have to shrink to the size of ants, creating all kinds of problems!

title: Carl
description: A pleasant weekend goes awry when a monster attacks.

title: The Potion
description: Gumball and Darwin learn that Hector is not so happy being giant-sized. So they decide to help him by creating a potion that will shrink him down to the size of an average person. However creating a magic potion is not as easy as it sounds, and the results can go spectacularly wrong...

title: The Thing in the Wall
description: When Axel and the team accuse Galileo of stealing their possessions, the lizard must hunt down the true culprit - a mysterious creature behind the wall - to prove his innocence.

title: The Traveler's Tree
description: Guilt-ridden over having lost the Traveler's Tea, Cole embarks on a dangerous quest to the top of a nearby mountain in hopes of finding the legendary Traveler's Tree - a tree which is supposedly guarded by a fearsome beast.

title: Krag's Lament
description: Cole awakens inside an icy cavern belonging to a legendary beast, and attempts to escape, only to discover a surprising truth.

title: Collection Infection
description: Having pared down their Magisword collection, the Warriors are forced into unconventional battle choices on a dangerous mission into the Deepest Darkest Woods.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Buttercup vs. Math
description: When Buttercup tests into Honors Math, she tries to avoid being labeled a nerd.

title: Mi Enemigo, Mi Amigo
description: El terrible Dragón de Hielo del Emperador ataca de nuevo, arrasando la aldea de los Pescadores de Hielo, obligando a los ninjas a seguir los pasos de Lloyd.

title: Conquistando torres
description: Duncan, Leshawna y Jude quieren una pieza de esquina del pastel de cumpleaños de Izzy, pero, ¿están preparados para hacer cualquier cosa por conseguir uno?

title: In the Doghouse
description: Buttercup must go it alone to save her family from a kidnapping.

title: New Beds
description: The guys get new beds.

title: Drawn to Sports with Olivia
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Olivia is a tennis player who is also passionate about art.

title: Arrested Development
description: Ben and Rook must stop the evil Robots from Dimension 12 while trapped in their own pre-pubescent bodies, thanks to Ben's childhood rival.  (Introducing Billy Billions.)

title: Journey to Maize Mountain Part 2
description: When Victor and Valentino destroy Monte Macabre's corn supply, they journey to Maíz Mountain with Sal to replace it. But in order to get the corn, they must shrink down to the size of ants and embark on a mythical adventure that they'll never forget!

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Fright Wig
description: When the King cannot overcome his fears, he abuses having the Sheriff's Dept. on call.

title: Wynton's Reality Show/Bakugan Soccer
description: Wynton's Reality Show: Lia has had it with Wynton's pranking, but little does she know Wynton is in for a taste of his own medicine. A prank goes too far, and Wynton finds himself in a real-life nightmare with a rampaging Bakugan!/Bakugan Soccer: The Awesome Brawlers and their Bakugan decide to have a game of Bakugan Soccer! The intensity ramps up when Pepe, his teammates and a mysterious coach show up for a little fun. It will take major teamwork for the Awesome Brawlers Bakugan to defeat this rowdy bunch.

title: Peluca de Terror
description: Cuando el rey no logra superar sus miedos, se abusa de la ventaja que le da tener al departamento del sheriff de guardia.

title: La Cosa en la Pared
description: Cuando Axel y el equipo acusan a Galileo de robar sus posesiones, el lagarto debe cazar al verdadero culpable, una misteriosa criatura detrás del muro, para demostrar su inocencia.

title: Claudus
description: Lion-O's dad King Claudus arrives on Third Earth, and turns out to be a big selfish jerk! Now Lion-O has to deal with his dad before he goes to war with the rest of the Thundercats.

title: The Escape Room of Doom
description: The gang infiltrate an escape room game center to thwart Score Creeper, but their former foe claims he only works there to pay the bills.

title: Los Opuestos se Atraen
description: Afirmando que es bueno de corazón, Dynamo convence a Axel y al equipo para que lo ayuden a encontrar una batería que pueda alimentar su centrífuga y liberarlo del control de Madtrap, pero Bobbie Blobby no está comprando la historia del malo.

title: French Fries
description: As a football craze sweeps the neighborhood, Daffy feels a slight over a Porky's French fry pilferage.

title: Many Happy Returns
description: Gwen and Kevin pay Ben a surprise visit, but does Kevin's strange behavior have anything to do with an angry Tetramand princess, or her father's fleet of warships prepared to attack the Earth?

title: Grin and Bear It
description: When a toothache sends Axel to the dentist, the team must fight off Princess SugarSalt, who confuses Axel's new "crown" for the real thing.

title: #TheGreenRoom
description: When Jessica is faced with a Green Lantern Corps disciplinary hearing, Hal appoints himself to be her Peer Advocate.

title: Malefactor
description: Khyber and his dog attacks Ben and Rook while they're at the "Olde Bellwood Days" festival, but does the hunter have other plans? (Introducing new Nemetrix alien Hypnotick.)

title: La Trampa de Madcap
description: Madcap y Princess SugarSalt atrapan a Axel y al equipo dentro de un laberinto impulsado por Minergy que los ataca con sus mayores temores, obligándolos a trabajar juntos y escapar como una unidad.

title: Radical Rescue
description: Rad is forced to reconsider his identity when KO starts taking on some of his traits.

title: Ballroom
description: MG fixes up the ballroom and warns UG and PS not to step a foot in there until he gets a chance to use it.  But UG mistakenly tosses a ball into the room.  Now PS and UG have to retrieve the ball without touching one foot to the ground.

title: Tourist Trap
description: While messing with the World's Largest Rubberband Ball at a tourist trap, Ben accidently releases some mischievous electrical creatures.

title: Pet Shop
description: Pet Shop tells the tale of where the Baby Bears once lived, and after a run-in with a video crew shooting a Sarah McLachlan-type animal adoption video, almost seized an opportunity to find a home separated from each other.

title: Apple's Focus
description: Apple helps Onion achieve his dream of competing on a baking show.

title: Let's Get Shadowy
description: KO teams up with an unlikely ally to take on an old foe.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Julian
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: La Pocion
description: Gumball y Darwin usan una poción mágica para encoger a Héctor.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: Hibernacion
description: Por ser un grupo urbano, los Osos jamás escucharon hablar de la idea de hibernar, hasta que Chloe les cuenta al respecto. Pardo, a quien le encanta la idea de comer mucho y luego dormir todo lo que se le dé la gana, se entrega a la hibernación sin pensarlo. Pero está tan entusiasmado con la idea de hibernar... que no se puede dormir.

title: Cupcake Job
description: When the Bears' beloved laptop breaks, they finally have the need to do something they've never done before: get jobs. Working at a trendy cupcake shop, the Bears find  that the working world is much tougher than they realized.

title: Perro Decisivo
description: Incapaz de tomar decisiones difíciles, Craig decide poner sus decisiones en manos de un perro llamado Fred.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: No Train No Gain
description: The guys help Pops train.

title: Sharing Is Caring
description: Courtney refuses to share her valuable collectors item toy with her classmates.

title: Sofa Cama
description: Cuando los Piratas del Cielo se infiltran en el cuartel general del sheriff, iponen en peligro a los héroes!

title: Burger's Trampoline
description: Apple and Onion must find a way to use Burger's trampoline without making him feel used.

title: Tienda De Mascotas
description: En este episodio sobre los primeros años de vida de los Osos, se cuenta la historia del lugar en el que vivieron alguna vez cuando eran bebés. Luego de un altercado con el equipo que filmaba un video absolutamente conmovedor de adopción de animales, los Osos por poco aprovechan la oportunidad de encontrar hogares alejados uno del otro.

title: Cy & Beasty
description: Cyborg and Beast Boy can't agree on the better character, Tom or Jerry, so they play a little game of cat and mouse.

title: Los Pajaros
description: When Valentino trades Huitzi's gifts for one of his own, the birds in town start to turn on him.

title: Chloe Y Polar
description: Un día, Chloe sale sola a pasear con Polar y se da cuenta de que Polar se la pasa haciéndoles recados a sus hermanos. Decidida a mostrarle cómo pasarla bien en la ciudad, Chloe promete ayudar a que Polar se divierta... Aunque eso signifique quedarse dentro de un museo después de la hora de cierre.

title: Fiesta en la Cuadra
